title: Panorama S56E07 Bottled Water Who Needs It WS PDTV XviD REMAX
description:
Reporter Tom Heap sets out to discover if the popularity of bottled
   water is a triumph of marketing over common sense and challenges UK
   consumers to end their love affair with the bottle. Environment
   Minister Phil Woolas says the amount of money spent on bottled water
   in the UK is approaching \&#039;morally unacceptable\&#039; levels. He is urging
   consumers - who spend 2 billion a year on bottled water - to go back
   to the tap.
